{"tid":2425611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"CCTVB 認證蛋糕藍店，整動漫蛋糕唔知洗唔洗版權呢？","createTime":"2021-02-27T12:43:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T16:07:46.000Z","uid":91228,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"0518c5d765e08ae0e7414fb982de59592702c1b7","tid":2425611,"uid":91228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T12:43:38.000Z","msg":"今晚有東張西望嘅認證<br />\n平時又有愛蝈政協陳小春，同一班CCTVB偽人認證嘅藍店<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UDmhJKb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUDmhJKb.png&h=edc455e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/98MUL1h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F98MUL1h.png&h=693e76b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WgJ4oOk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWgJ4oOk.png&h=f7c44954&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知整咁多Disney，任天堂，鬼滅嘅蛋糕拎去賣洗唔洗攞版權呢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bRR5SHc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbRR5SHc.png&h=cc366db9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2w7dg8T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2w7dg8T.png&h=521efccd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BHtPzVA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBHtPzVA.png&h=359c452d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ePcwOfB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FePcwOfB.png&h=8a72f2e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蛋糕店出售的立體卡通蛋糕，雖然未必會與正版的卡通人物一模一樣，惟在法律上而言，原來只要兩者之間有相似的地方，而一般人又能輕易辨識到，相關蛋糕店就有機會被控侵權。<br />\n<br />\n「似同唔似之間，其實好少存在灰色地帶。」法律界人士黃國桐指出，以卡通人物為例，一般人對該類卡通人物的特徵都有認識，複製品很容易就會聯想到原來的卡通人物，因此，很少案件會有人以相似程度作抗辯理由。<br />\n<br />\n「對於似同唔似呢個問題，法官一般會搵唔同行業嘅專家協助。」鄧達明則補充，以立體卡通蛋糕為例，法庭有機會要求卡通設計師，對物品的相似度作出分析。此外，法官亦會同時考慮一般人角度，從而決定該案件有否涉及侵權。<br />\n（from 白粉報唔貼link）"},{"pid":"c468cc1527ac5e2fb0590b1b129a455e4949c75b","tid":2425611,"uid":3020,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T12:45:42.000Z","msg":"要版權<br />\n<br />\n參考迪士尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a8394322db371836aaac4b3a52b7abe368da527","tid":2425611,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T12:52:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"18621a7a15d02648c18519077330540e55d5d77c","tid":2425611,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T12:53:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0ae4cff3e3025a881fb86a07979448e7a7a2371d","tid":2425611,"uid":140793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T12:54:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8ac6a57db7d9daf8190f37aaf4b67de95fcd54ed","tid":2425611,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T12:55:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb18a792f79a6444e97958c76c227b765d6e6e3d","tid":2425611,"uid":121425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T12:55:28.000Z","msg":"嗯，一人一信掟去集英、UFO、迪迪尼？<br />\n總有一間會中嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cf578140481024cef0ba7dd652888e2bdfaa3db","tid":2425611,"uid":24457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T12:56:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a91f4954a37c7cd6c1635d3e5e2c0a8bd14a74c5","tid":2425611,"uid":53062,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T12:56:10.000Z","msg":"政治我唔識，總之侵權就係唔岩"},{"pi